[SN]TITLE[SN]
Death of man in street in Croftfoot 'suspicious'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Police are treating the death of a man who was found seriously injured in a Glasgow street as suspicious.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Officers were called to reports of a disturbance in Midcroft Avenue, near its junction with Ashcroft Drive, in the city's Croftfoot area at 02:25.
The injured man died at the scene a short time later.
Police Scotland said they were trying to establish the man's identity and a post mortem examination would be carried out to establish how he died.
